messages.content: This is your chance to make a real difference, vote for a party that supports all people not just the privileged few.

keyPolicies.policyDescription: Labour will deliver a green economy, good for the environment, for jobs and for all our futures. Labour will abolish unfair letting fees and commit to building new houses, so we will have the chance of our own homes.

mentions.tacticalSituation: Only Labour can beat the Conservatives. Vote Labour with me

issues.economy: Labour will deliver a green economy, good for the environment, for jobs and for all our futures.
issues.environment: Labour will deliver a green economy, good for the environment.
issues.governance: Labour's core values of equality, liberty and fairness are reflected in their policies.

housing.content: Labour will abolish unfair letting fees and commit to building new houses, so we will have the chance of our own homes.
